divs: Sighting DetailsI was sound asleep and awakened with sharp pain in left knee and femoral area of left hip. Did not see anyone, sounds or lights - just pain in left leg and ugly purple bruises. Husband was asleep in his chair and dog asleep in doorway. I think something grabbed my legs and roughly moved me. I am a 75 year old retired health professional.
